@DATABASE "Sweevo's World"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - S - Sweevo's World"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - S
                   ====================================

                              Sweevo's World
                              ==============



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Lives = x      " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(24858,255) ZXAMPoke(36957,255)"}         24858,x:36957,x (x= 1-255)
@{"Infinite Lives " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(33122,182)"}         33122,182
@{"Infinite Ouches" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(33599,182)"}         33599,182

                         Another POKE by me, since the one with ZXAMPoke
                         didn't work.

                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         Rastan.
@endnode
